      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. SHEEZEL is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 20.13 beating Keiki Polu. Looks to have an edge on most of these. 4. BIG BUCKETS fast out of the inside draw with a slick early sectional and clocking 23.43 in a one length win at Casino over 411m last time. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. 2. CASH IN COLOUR turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.28) at this track behind Nitro Slim in a Mix 2/3. Has the pace to be prominent. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Can feature again. 8. KEIKI POLU was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage second (20.20) at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw.\",\"runners\":[5,4,2,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
